message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11,000. It's a fantastic deal and I know you'll find it very valuable. Let me know what you think!
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the value of the product, but I can only pay up to $9,500 for it. I hope we can come to an agreement.

Bob, I appreciate your offer but I need to be closer to $10,500 to make this work for me. It's a fantastic product and I'm sure you'll find it worth the investment. Let's find a price that works for both of us.
